	<internal-name>Intro</internal-name>
	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-top</sectionClass_s>
	<file-name>67c64c5a-cfcb-a272-d63a-36246ba8a53f.xml</file-name>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;This is not a scam, really. SARS desperately wants to refund you a portion of the tax you had to pay so you can use the money for things you actually want to pay for such as taking a short left, renovating your family home or even putting down a deposit on those wheels you have been eyeing for some time now. Let&amp;rsquo;s see if we can answer the questions that had you thinking &amp;ldquo;Impossible. Scam alert&amp;rdquo; !&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;How is this even possible?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;By contributing towards a retirement product (such as your employer&amp;rsquo;s pension fund, provident fund or a separate retirement annuity, RA for short), SARS will calculate the tax you need to pay based on your income MINUS any contributions you have made. In other words, any money that you put into a retirement product, will be deducted from your taxable income resulting in less tax payable by you.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
